{"tid":1764280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【TVB合約戰，最後11日！】 終極洗版任務 - 課金共７億廣告大戶 (第七回合)","createTime":"2019-12-01T04:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T18:09:05.000Z","uid":267969,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"530b0a4797026ecf6fe6bd08709855d8add3a4f3","tid":1764280,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12月12日*，就係TVB 2020年廣告簽約deadline<br />\n廣告商一旦簽約，TVB穩賺！</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>最後11日</strong></span></span>，我哋精選咗50大廣告商，每日俾大家瘋狂洗版+電郵！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求下你哋唔好放過TVB！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">*12月12日係early bird deadline，12月13日為真deadline</span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【終極任務 - 第七回合@1 Dec 2019 】</span></strong> </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4C0drwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4C0drwx.jpg&h=0a6c2030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>洗版行動</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong>1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5. 互like留言，推上FB留言熱門</strong><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1️⃣幸福醫藥 2️⃣美素佳兒 3️⃣雙飛人藥水<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFortune.Pharmacal&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=a5c09179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/frisohk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffrisohk&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=1fa14faf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/frisohk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/peppermintcure\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpeppermintcure&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=9efabc69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/peppermintcure</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幸福醫藥課金排名第一!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2019年落咗近3億廣告!!</span></span><br />\n買藥買咁貴，原來啲錢去晒CCTVB到做廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美素佳兒都唔差，排第五落左近2億廣告!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※留言template</strong></span></span><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，或未能即時撤回廣告。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>電郵行動</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一次過Send Email最有效!!<br />\n電郵清單及範本<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XVYXVk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XVYXVk&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=a919d995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XVYXVk</a><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">想補做/一次過做任務嘅戰士，睇呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<blockquote>終極洗版任務 - <span style=\"color: red;\">夜晚時段由teammate黃心穎(回魂)</span> 發放<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/75759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/75759</a><br />\n<br />\n50大廣告商任務時間表<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ryhivM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ryhivM&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0BzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=6b7c0d29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ryhivM</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">歡迎用呢幾幅圖去FB留言</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&h=ffeb70a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/76722773_506597276863793_238195025060560896_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ohc=hFCuwrpCqa4AQlmbyG1aclGzX_utc1CzVGjlWUOrJmDgvVCzcwrwIhm1w&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=11623860420d69157bb9452c83b4d183&amp;oe=5E7B3B77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F76722773_506597276863793_238195025060560896_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ohc%3DhFCuwrpCqa4AQlmbyG1aclGzX_utc1CzVGjlWUOrJmDgvVCzcwrwIhm1w%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D11623860420d69157bb9452c83b4d183%26oe%3D5E7B3B77&h=3dc1a50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/74224155_490378655152322_791355193236127744_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_ohc=tXIxhMQsJ8UAQn4XB5G7r8mn8u5uB-ULY4irvoTHfKXU_0-_Ok2g4lnMw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=df2d1655aeb87c638b079af9398bccec&amp;oe=5E49C4DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?